N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6 ยง 637.12 - Examinations

State Regulations

The commissioner may require any person whose qualifications are submitted for consideration to take written, oral or practical examinations, and may approve such qualifications in a specific grade on the basis of the results of such examinations. Notes
